name: Arab Latice
description: Digital token of physical piece of art handmade by Metakupol (metakupol.com) @Metakupol -- Representing the Air and linked to The Heart Chakra the Octahedron is the third shape in the series of the five Platonic Solids. Structurally made from eight faces, six vertices and twelve edges. The symmetry of the shape consists in eight triangles that form two square based pyramids. In the nature we can note this shape in many crystals such as Diamond, Magnetite, Fluorite to name a few examples.
